{
  "stem": "1828.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 239.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- things became worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a German presence in the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Czechs walked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They demonstrated, and cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did not wear their uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Hitler Youth uniforms were not seen at first, at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, there was a sprinkling of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They refused to join.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many were arrested and persecuted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- a was very tense time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the ghetto came into focus-- Theresienstadt, which was a-- where they kept group-- groups of the military, which housed about 8,000 people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's where the transports started going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Prior to that, I had joined the Bnei Akiva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were organized to help the older people who had to go into transports, to help them with their belongings, and to advise them of what not to try to take at all, and what to leave behind, and what they could carry.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and that was very sobering, because you learned so much ahead of time what was coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I knew what had-- we heard all kind of reports.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew what it was like, roughly, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we knew one of these days they were going to call us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father, his chavrusa, his learning partner, when we were called, decided that rather than take a chance of the Nazis cutting his beard in their own way-- that was a very emotional moment.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They went to the bathroom and he asked him to shave his beard off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He looked entirely different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKING] [CRYING] Theresienstadt was a-- was an hour away by-- by train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when I arrived there, I had friends waiting for me there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They knew we were coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had lists of who's coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We always stayed together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
